{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.440", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.520", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.560", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Interessant ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.200", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Bartsch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.360", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie immer bei den gro\u00dfen Unternehmen mit Gesetzentw\u00fcrfen kommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.361", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcrde mir w\u00fcnschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.361", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.362", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir insgesamt \u00fcber die allgemeine Gemengelage reden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.362", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.680", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcbrigens auch \u00fcber Insolvenzen von kleineren Unternehmen\u00a0\u2013"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.720", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sind \u00fcbrigens 58 am Tag; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.000", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dar\u00fcber wird viel zu wenig gesprochen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.200", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir aus unseren Wahlkreisen kennen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.320", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei denen betroffene Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeiter zu uns kommen und mit uns reden"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.800", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir sp\u00fcren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.720", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es nicht nur um die Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeiter geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.640", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch um Familien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.120", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um ganze Regionen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.240", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erst gestern noch habe ich mit Stanislaw Tillich gesprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.920", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er hat mir nat\u00fcrlich die Auswirkungen auf die Situation in G\u00f6rlitz skizziert; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.921", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dabei ging es nicht nur um die drohende Schlie\u00dfung des Werkes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.921", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.922", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern nat\u00fcrlich auch um die Auswirkungen auf die Zulieferindustrie."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.922", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.923", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber in dieser Situation trotzdem bitte k\u00fchlen Kopf bewahren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.923", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.924", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr Gesetzentwurf entspricht dem nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.924", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.925", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eK\u00fchlen Kopf bewahren\u201c hei\u00dft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.925", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.926", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir Politik und Wirtschaft trennen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.926", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.927", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir als Politiker f\u00fcr die politischen Entscheidungen zust\u00e4ndig sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.927", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.928", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es diesem Land auch in 10, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.928", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.929", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "15\u00a0Jahren noch gut geht,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.929", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.040", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dass die Wirtschaft betriebswirtschaftlich entscheidet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.400", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nehmen Sie nur mal das Beispiel der Digitalisierung und Disruption! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.401", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bedenken Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.401", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.520", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir da f\u00fcr Ver\u00e4nderungen haben\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Bereich des Verlagswesens, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.840", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Bereich des Anlagenbaus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.080", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Maschinenbau bis hin zum Bereich Elektro! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.360", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da werden ganze Gesch\u00e4ftsmodelle infrage gestellt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.760", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Unternehmer m\u00fcssen entscheiden: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.360", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie sieht das Gesch\u00e4ftsmodell der Zukunft aus? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.760", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind unternehmerische, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.400", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "betriebliche Entscheidungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.480", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da hat sich die Politik nicht einzumischen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.840", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber genau das machen Sie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.960", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie mischen sich ein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allein die Debatte dar\u00fcber ist nicht gut f\u00fcr den Investitionsstandort Deutschland."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.040", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Mittelstand und in energieintensiven Bereichen wird heute schon mehr abgeschrieben als investiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.600", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daher ist das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.800", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Sie machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.801", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "falsch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.801", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.440", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Kern sorgt Ihr Gesetz daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.800", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass nicht die Konzerne, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.801", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern die Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeiter die Leidtragenden sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.801", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.802", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie sich so einmischen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.802", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.803", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werden nicht nur Werke geschlossen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.803", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.804", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern ganze Unternehmen ins Ausland verlegt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.804", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.200", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann sind die Arbeitnehmerinnen und Arbeitnehmer wirklich die Leidtragenden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.440", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sollten sie aber nicht sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.240", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie mich einen ganz anderen Punkt ansprechen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.800", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der in der sozialen Marktwirtschaft wichtiger denn je ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.200", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist die Verantwortung der Unternehmer gegen\u00fcber Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeitern jenseits unternehmerischer Entscheidungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.480", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich hat die Wirtschaft auch eine gesellschaftliche Verantwortung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.080", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist sicherlich zu kritisieren\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.000", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch daf\u00fcr ist dieses Haus da\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.920", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeiter erst nach Tagen oder sogar Wochen aus Berichten in Medien erfahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.040", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es um ihre Zukunft bestellt ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.160", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist nicht der Weg, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.520", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den die soziale Marktwirtschaft vorsieht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.840", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielmehr muss es um Gemeinsamkeit gehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.480", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch bei schwierigen Entscheidungen m\u00fcssen die Arbeitnehmerinnen und Arbeitnehmer mitgenommen werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.400", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist nicht zuletzt deshalb wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.880", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die Wirtschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.800", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie im Corporate Governance Kodex festgelegt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.280", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich bin froh, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.640", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es in diesem Land einen Konsens dazu gibt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.720", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine gesellschaftliche Verantwortung gegen\u00fcber den Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeitern hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.280", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie muss also bei schwierigen Entscheidungen die Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeiter mitnehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.520", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht zuletzt das ist es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.480", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "worauf es ankommt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.560", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meines Erachtens hat Siemens nun die Chance, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.440", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Gespr\u00e4ch zu suchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.040", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir als Politiker k\u00f6nnen flankieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.041", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "moderieren und viele Gespr\u00e4che f\u00fchren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.041", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.042", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber am Ende d\u00fcrfen wir uns nicht in unternehmerische Entscheidungen einmischen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.042", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.120", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege Linnemann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.000", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "jetzt haben Sie eine Zwischenfrage des Kollegen Ernst verpasst."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.160", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Sie k\u00f6nnen jederzeit eine Kurzintervention machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.440", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie das m\u00f6chten.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.000", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann machen Sie es."
   ]
  }
 ]
}